### Post a new order
POST localhost:8080/api/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "address": "123 Main St, Ann Arbor, MI 48109",
  "restaurantId": 4,
  "items": [
    {
      "idItem": 11,
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 55
    },
    {
      "idItem": 12,
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 35
    }
  ],

  "status": "CREATED"
}

### Update order
PUT localhost:8080/api/order/id/6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 6,
  "userId": 1,
  "address": "123 Main St, Ann Arbor, MI 48109",
  "restaurantId": 4,
  "items": [
    {
      "idItem": 11,
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 55
    },
    {
      "idItem": 12,
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 35
    }
  ],

  "status": "DELIVERING"
}

### Get order by id
GET localhost:8080/api/order/id/6
Accept: application/json

### Get orders by user id
GET localhost:8080/api/order/userId/1
Accept: application/json